## Requirements

- macOS 14 (Sonoma) or later
- Apple Silicon Mac (M1/M2/M3/M4/M5)

## Installation

1. Download `wskrs.zip` from the [Releases](../../releases) page
2. Extract the zip file
3. Drag `wskrs.app` to your **Applications** folder
4. **First launch**: Right-click the app â†’ select "Open" â†’ click "Open" in the dialog
   > This is required because Whiskers is not yet signed with an Apple Developer ID

## How It Works

1. **Hold Fn** to start recording
2. **Speak** your text
3. **Release** to transcribe and paste into current application

Whiskers runs entirely on your Mac â€” no internet connection required, no data leaves your device.

